summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1915, for the improvement of Sixth Avenue West from West Galer Street to West Comstock Street and from West Highland Drive to West Prospect Street; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues therein named, all in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete walks thereon, under Ordinance No. 19770, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
